siders the complex case of the seven-time champion Lance Armstrong.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 24. Mai 2022) 0aBicycle racingxSocial aspectszFrance. 7aSPORTS & RECREATION / History.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertUniversity of California Press Backlist Package 2000-2013z978311069042240uhttps://doi.org/10.1525/978052093285240uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780520932852423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780520932852/original  a978-3-11-069042-2  University of California Press Backlist Package 2000-2013c2000d2013  aEBA_FAO  aEBA_UCA_YUP  aGBV-deGruyter-alles